data.table mapping zips and census tracts

census_tract_zip_crosswalk.Rd

Data are stored at extdata/ZIP_TRACT_062021.xlsx for convenience. They were accesses on September 25, 2021.

census_tract_zip_crosswalk()

Source

https://www.huduser.gov/portal/datasets/usps_crosswalk.html

Geographic level

  • zipcode

  • census tract

Download

  • https://github.com/seandavi/UCCCReporter/raw/main/inst/extdata/ZIP_TRACT_062021.xlsx

See also

Other Data resources: rural_zips(), zipcode_shapes()

ctract_zip = census_tract_zip_crosswalk()
